title: 07/30/21 DPS Hour 1 Dan Orlovsky

description:
Dan Orlovsky tells Dan that he would rather be late than early to the Deshaun Watson party. Orlovsky says the Rams will be the more interesting story in Los Angeles, but that the Chargers are coming.
